<p style="padding-bottom: 0px;">
    ABA Bank issued corporate bonds (ABA Bond) worth KHR 84.821 billion (around USD 21 million) with the nominal amount of KHR 100,000 per bond and the maturity of three years. The coupon rate is 7.75% p.a. with
    the semi-annual coupon payment. The Bond is available for both institutional and retail investors.
</p>
